project_descr: To Support the country response to address challenges related to Tuberculosis, Malaria, HIV/AIDS and Health system weaknesses.

donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS
outputs.output_descr: Malaria in Sudan is unstable and highly variable geographically and seasonally in intensity of transmission. Transmission is highest in the southern part of the country and risk is also high in irrigated areas.
